1
00:00:15,590 --> 00:00:16,990
Greetings, Princess Fu.

2
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:19,620
Our Princess Consort
invites you for a chat.

3
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:33,960
Her Highness is waiting for you inside.

4
00:00:41,070 --> 00:00:42,000
Zhao Chun'er.

5
00:00:42,790 --> 00:00:44,450
Why did you ask me to come here?

6
00:00:48,470 --> 00:00:51,670
Her Majesty asked me to show you
the people you want to see—

7
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:52,920
your friends.

8
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:00,430
Lin Mu?

9
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,390
Lin Mu!

10
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:07,580
Your Highness!

11
00:01:07,950 --> 00:01:09,550
-Your Highness?
-Your Highness?

12
00:01:09,550 --> 00:01:10,260
Your Highness.

13
00:01:10,260 --> 00:01:11,520
How are your injuries?

14
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:13,150
We're fine.

15
00:01:13,950 --> 00:01:15,350
Don't be sad, Your Highness.

16
00:01:15,350 --> 00:01:16,710
I'm strong.

17
00:01:18,590 --> 00:01:19,650
I won't die easily.

18
00:01:20,230 --> 00:01:20,950
Zhao Chun'er!

19
00:01:20,950 --> 00:01:22,350
What exactly do you want?

20
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:26,770
What can a weak woman like me do?

21
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,230
I just know you.

22
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,090
I know you value friendship

23
00:01:31,230 --> 00:01:33,479
and that you must be very worried about
your friends,

24
00:01:33,479 --> 00:01:35,280
so I brought you here to see them.

25
00:01:35,710 --> 00:01:37,070
Shouldn't you thank me?

26
00:01:38,039 --> 00:01:38,759
After all,

27
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:41,590
they were captured because of you.

28
00:01:42,590 --> 00:01:45,039
And they might even die because of you.

29
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:47,420
This meeting today

30
00:01:48,110 --> 00:01:49,880
might be your last.

31
00:01:52,170 --> 00:01:53,009
Come at me!

32
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:54,750
They've done nothing to you!

33
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:56,430
Yes.

34
00:01:57,670 --> 00:01:58,870
I am coming at you.

35
00:01:59,150 --> 00:02:00,150
If it weren't for you,

36
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:02,280
they wouldn't have ended up like this.

37
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,540
For the sake of our old acquaintance,

38
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,640
I'll show you a clear path.

39
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,240
If you agree to marry Yan Xun,

40
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:10,770
Her Majesty will agree to let them go.

41
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:13,120
Otherwise, they will be branded

42
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,520
as traitors just like you

43
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,870
and Li Ce,

44
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,310
and executed.

45
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:18,000
Your Highness!

46
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,120
Don't agree!

47
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:21,800
So?

48
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:25,010
Haven't you always prided yourself
on being great?

49
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,280
What are you hesitating for?

50
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,400
Do you want to stay here

51
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,190
and keep watching them suffer!

52
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,030
Zhao Chun'er!

53
00:02:32,050 --> 00:02:33,780
Living a life worse than death?

54
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:35,520
I don't understand.

55
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,079
Why must you make me marry Yan Xun?

56
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:38,190
Don't you like him?

57
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,450
Why are you doing this?

58
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:42,840
Do you think I still care about Yan Xun?

59
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:46,360
Have you forgotten what I told you?

60
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,690
I just want you to be miserable.

61
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,560
I want you to watch the people around you

62
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,180
get implicated because of you

63
00:02:52,180 --> 00:02:53,420
and suffer.

64
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,280
Open the door!

65
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,740
Because you're a jinx,

66
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:01,470
everyone around you

67
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:03,000
will be dragged down by you.

68
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,590
Are you going to agree or not?

69
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:06,590
Are you going to open the door or not?

70
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:38,510
Zhao Chun'er,

71
00:03:39,370 --> 00:03:40,650
you are truly insane.

72
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:47,320
I am the future Queen of Great Yan!

73
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,720
Who dares to be insolent?

74
00:03:50,329 --> 00:03:50,960
Stop!

75
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,360
Chun'er.

76
00:04:04,310 --> 00:04:05,240
Are you alright?

77
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,100
Your Highness,

78
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,120
you're here.

79
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:12,040
Princess Fu,

80
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:13,960
let's leave it here for today.

81
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:16,019
Don't blow things out of proportion.

82
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:22,870
Brothers,

83
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:25,020
I will definitely rescue you.

84
00:05:51,550 --> 00:05:56,720
[REBIRTH]

85
00:05:57,250 --> 00:05:59,650
[Episode 18]

86
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:08,920
Lady Chu,

87
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,000
can we talk upstairs?

88
00:06:11,310 --> 00:06:13,510
What do you want with me, General Cheng?

89
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:15,270
Trying to kill me again?

90
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,860
I have no personal grudge against you.

91
00:06:20,860 --> 00:06:21,690
We were on opposite sides before

92
00:06:21,690 --> 00:06:23,510
just because of different positions.

93
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:25,040
That's not the case anymore.

94
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,280
We now share the same interests,

95
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:27,750
so we can put aside our differences

96
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:29,350
and talk about cooperation.

97
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,659
I can help you escape from Yan Xun.

98
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,190
What are you up to?

99
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:44,870
I don't care about you.

100
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:48,270
I just don't want to see Yan Xun

101
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:50,960
become more and more crazy because of you.

102
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:52,070
What I want

103
00:06:52,909 --> 00:06:55,200
is a wise King of Great Yan.

104
00:06:55,830 --> 00:06:57,360
Why are you telling me this?

105
00:06:57,480 --> 00:07:00,280
Because you are the only one
who can influence him.

106
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,070
If you leave him,

107
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:05,600
it might make him less arrogant and cruel.

108
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:08,730
That would be a good thing
for me and the entire Great Yan.

109
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,840
How do you want to cooperate?

110
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:28,430
You are not fully recovered.

111
00:07:28,430 --> 00:07:30,360
Stay a few more days
and recover before you leave.

112
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,420
You should give me what you promised.

113
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:57,170
King Ximeng wants me to take your life.

114
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:58,600
I can't die yet.

115
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,830
If you don't die,

116
00:08:00,350 --> 00:08:01,990
my tribe and I will!

117
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,600
Your poison is acting up.

118
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,730
Rather than suffer,

119
00:08:28,150 --> 00:08:29,750
I might as well end it for you.

120
00:08:32,909 --> 00:08:34,820
Your injuries are not fully recovered yet.

121
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,059
If we fight now,

122
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:38,000
I won't let you go back alive.

123
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,780
He has no antidote.

124
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:41,440
He won't last more than a few days.

125
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,970
Stay with him while you can.

126
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,720
Zhuge Yue?

127
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,870
Zhuge Yue! Zhuge Yue!

128
00:08:52,710 --> 00:08:54,280
Zhuge Yue, wake up!

129
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:56,000
Zhuge Yue...

130
00:08:57,310 --> 00:08:58,080
wake up.

131
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:04,390
Chun'er!

132
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,310
What exactly do you want?

133
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,790
You've already achieved your goal.

134
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:09,390
Why did you provoke Chu Qiao?

135
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:11,240
Chun'er,

136
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,780
you weren't like this before.

137
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:16,320
Ever since you met Chu Qiao,
you've become...

138
00:09:17,670 --> 00:09:18,480
Go on.

139
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,140
What have I become?

140
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,820
You've become twisted and terrifying,

141
00:09:21,820 --> 00:09:23,620
nothing like the Chun'er I knew.

142
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,320
Li Yan,

143
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,550
you're right.

144
00:09:32,110 --> 00:09:33,570
You are absolutely right.

145
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,080
Every time I see Chu Qiao,

146
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,210
I feel like I'm trapped in a nightmare.

147
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:39,750
In that nightmare,

148
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,320
I'm a hideous monster!

149
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,850
I'm sorry, Chun'er.

150
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,530
I shouldn't have said that.

151
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,780
You are not a hideous monster.

152
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,930
You're the person I treasure most.

153
00:09:53,790 --> 00:09:54,480
Li Yan,

154
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,460
you don't understand.

155
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:59,070
You're loving the wrong person.

156
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:01,720
You never truly knew me.

157
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:06,000
I've always been ugly

158
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,670
and broken.

159
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:11,030
The Chun'er you loved

160
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,000
was killed by Yan Xun long ago.

161
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:17,360
On the day of my wedding,

162
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,790
the moment he rebelled,

163
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:21,550
he killed me once mercilessly.

164
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,760
In the reed marshes of Great Yan,

165
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:26,080
those soldiers humiliated me

166
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,660
and trampled on me.

167
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:30,440
That was when I died all over again.

168
00:10:30,930 --> 00:10:32,560
Chun'er, say no more.

169
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:36,030
Chu Qiao saw it with her own eyes!

170
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:38,910
She saw my most humiliating moment.

171
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:41,550
I hate her so much.

172
00:10:41,810 --> 00:10:42,760
Why?

173
00:10:44,030 --> 00:10:45,960
Why could she, just a slave,

174
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:48,340
act so high and mighty

175
00:10:48,370 --> 00:10:50,250
while she watched me get pinned down
and humiliated

176
00:10:50,250 --> 00:10:51,580
by those people?

177
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,980
Why was it so easy for a slave like her

178
00:10:53,980 --> 00:10:56,650
to ruin my life?

179
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:02,120
Li Yan,

180
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,600
you didn't expect this, did you?

181
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,840
The Chun'er you like

182
00:11:06,150 --> 00:11:07,670
is a naked,

183
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:10,240
filthy monster.

184
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:13,970
If you regret it now...

185
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,670
Chun'er!

186
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,120
Chun'er!

187
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,360
No matter what you've been through,

188
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:22,240
I will not leave you.

189
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:26,030
I am willing to love
every one of your wounds

190
00:11:26,550 --> 00:11:28,480
and endure the suffering with you.

191
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:37,030
Will you really not despise me?

192
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:37,910
Chun'er,

193
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,900
no matter what kind of person you are,

194
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,540
I will always stay with you

195
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,170
for the rest of my life.

196
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,660
For all those who wronged you,

197
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:50,480
I will make them pay double for you.

198
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:04,930
[Qifeng Palace]

199
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,150
Your Majesty.

200
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,440
I'll marry Yan Xun.

201
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,670
I knew you would come.

202
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:39,360
I like making deals with smart people.

203
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:40,750
Then I still can't

204
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,270
compare to you.

205
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:44,390
I can marry Yan Xun for Li Ce's sake.

206
00:12:44,750 --> 00:12:45,720
But you

207
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:47,050
can kill your own child

208
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,910
for the sake of power.

209
00:13:00,910 --> 00:13:02,910
You have so many scars on your hands.

210
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,510
Does it hurt?

211
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:10,050
Thank you for your concern, Your Majesty.

212
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:11,840
They are old wounds.

213
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:13,910
They don't hurt anymore.

214
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:15,120
A woman's hands

215
00:13:15,140 --> 00:13:16,570
must be beautiful.

216
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,290
What are you afraid of, General Chu?

217
00:13:38,290 --> 00:13:39,750
This White Jade Suet Cream

218
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,550
is made from the fat extracted

219
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,360
from the tenderest part

220
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:45,420
of newborn lambs in the Snowy Region.

221
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:48,080
It melts when applied to the hands.

222
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:51,010
It's the best thing
for moisturizing a woman's skin.

223
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:53,320
I'm going to tell you a story.

224
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:55,320
When you finish listening,

225
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:57,120
your hands will be moisturized.

226
00:13:59,950 --> 00:14:01,640
There once was a woman.

227
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:04,550
Her husband fought with his brother
over the family inheritance

228
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:05,910
and was killed.

229
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:09,270
The woman was pregnant.

230
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:12,080
To save her and her unborn child,

231
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:17,390
-she begged her brother-in-law for mercy.
-Your Highness!

232
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:19,080
I am willing to give up any status

233
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,600
to serve by your side.

234
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,320
She even gave herself to him,

235
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,850
hoping to use her sincerity

236
00:14:23,870 --> 00:14:26,200
in exchange for her and her child's lives.

237
00:14:26,670 --> 00:14:28,270
The man agreed.

238
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,870
He took her body

239
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:32,240
and claimed that

240
00:14:32,550 --> 00:14:34,210
he had fallen in love with her.

241
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:35,620
But secretly,

242
00:14:35,870 --> 00:14:37,750
he still had her child killed.

243
00:14:38,370 --> 00:14:41,440
From now on, you are my beloved concubine.

244
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:43,390
I will certainly keep

245
00:14:43,550 --> 00:14:44,510
my promise to you.

246
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:46,600
I will let his child grow up safely.

247
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:49,670
The Prince Consort of Chang is about
as far along in her pregnancy as you,

248
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:50,930
and she is due soon too.

249
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,880
Your Majesty, do you mean

250
00:14:53,900 --> 00:14:55,830
you want to send the child in my womb

251
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:58,320
to the Prince of Chang's Mansion
to be raised?

252
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,290
If the child is born and lives there

253
00:14:59,290 --> 00:15:01,800
as the son of the Prince of Chang,

254
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:03,070
when he grows up,

255
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:05,030
I will grant him official rank
and noble titles,

256
00:15:05,030 --> 00:15:07,550
and let him enjoy a life
of wealth and honor.

257
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:09,430
Your Majesty,

258
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:11,600
His Majesty has ordered me

259
00:15:11,890 --> 00:15:12,690
to take

260
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:14,660
the little Heir Apparent to the palace

261
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:17,660
for a routine pulse check
by the imperial physicians.

262
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:21,090
Just one little Heir Apparent?

263
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,030
Yes.

264
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:24,720
Just one.

265
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:27,440
Your Majesty!

266
00:15:28,510 --> 00:15:29,840
Yan Qing, what's wrong?

267
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,840
The little Heir Apparent

268
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,660
contracted the plague...

269
00:15:34,030 --> 00:15:35,320
and has passed away.

270
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:36,960
The man lied to the woman,

271
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:39,370
telling her the child died of illness.

272
00:15:40,150 --> 00:15:41,720
The woman knew he was lying,

273
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:43,420
but to survive,

274
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,940
she couldn't expose him.

275
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:47,510
She could only smile

276
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:49,200
and play along with him.

277
00:15:49,870 --> 00:15:50,670
Later,

278
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,480
this woman got pregnant again

279
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:55,390
and gave birth to the man's child.

280
00:15:55,790 --> 00:15:57,270
Looking at the child,

281
00:15:57,510 --> 00:15:58,840
she was in immense pain,

282
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:01,720
feeling that she had failed her child
who had died.

283
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:02,630
Day and night,

284
00:16:02,650 --> 00:16:04,150
she heard the cries

285
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:05,720
of the dead child.

286
00:16:23,030 --> 00:16:24,750
If you were this woman,

287
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:26,240
what would you do?

288
00:16:26,910 --> 00:16:27,840
What about Li Ce?

289
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,200
Isn't he innocent?

290
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,200
No matter how much suffering
you've endured,

291
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:32,720
you shouldn't

292
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:34,580
make him pay for your grievances.

293
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,120
Then tell me,

294
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:42,000
aren't the slaves of Qingshan Manor
in Great Yong

295
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,080
innocent?

296
00:16:43,790 --> 00:16:45,790
Aren't the soldiers
on the battlefield of Great Yan

297
00:16:45,790 --> 00:16:46,910
innocent?

298
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:48,240
Slaves

299
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,630
have the fate of slaves.

300
00:16:49,630 --> 00:16:51,630
Soldiers have the fate of soldiers.

301
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:53,720
As the crown prince of the royal family,

302
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:55,360
he also has his fate.

303
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:58,080
This is his fate,

304
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:02,870
and it is mine as well.

305
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,440
You simply don't understand

306
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,680
what men are,

307
00:17:08,109 --> 00:17:09,440
or what power is.

308
00:17:10,750 --> 00:17:11,720
Attachments

309
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:14,609
are meant to hold back fools
who trap themselves.

310
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,069
I became the Empress

311
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:20,180
not because His Majesty loved me so much,

312
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:22,530
but because I could do many things
for him,

313
00:17:23,069 --> 00:17:24,680
allowing him to rest easy.

314
00:17:25,069 --> 00:17:26,240
Do you think His Majesty doesn't know

315
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:29,350
there are many doubts about
the Crown Prince's assassination?

316
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:31,000
But his fear

317
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:32,960
is more important than anything else.

318
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:35,510
He would rather kill his own son
by mistake.

319
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,860
In the face of imperial power,

320
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:42,310
attachments

321
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:44,350
are not worth mentioning.

322
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:47,920
You don't have to hold a grudge
against His Majesty,

323
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:48,750
because you

324
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,310
are just like him.

325
00:17:50,790 --> 00:17:52,520
You are the same kind of people.

326
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:56,550
You're wrong.

327
00:17:58,310 --> 00:18:00,350
I have put a great deal of effort

328
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:02,790
into becoming like them.

329
00:18:03,350 --> 00:18:04,880
The Crown Prince is my son,

330
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,860
but more than that, he is a man.

331
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:10,750
I may not understand my son,

332
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:12,960
but in my life,

333
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:14,400
I have seen too many men,

334
00:18:14,830 --> 00:18:16,360
enough to understand them.

335
00:18:17,310 --> 00:18:18,350
I imitate them,

336
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:20,220
trying to become them,

337
00:18:20,510 --> 00:18:22,030
so that I can survive

338
00:18:22,030 --> 00:18:23,160
in this palace.

339
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,830
You may like Li Ce now.

340
00:18:26,590 --> 00:18:27,400
But that's only because

341
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,000
he hasn't seized power yet.

342
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,460
He still needs you.

343
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:33,440
Once he seizes power,

344
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:35,960
he will become
a completely different person.

345
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:38,350
Think of Yan Xun, whom you once helped.

346
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:40,110
I know Li Ce.

347
00:18:40,350 --> 00:18:41,550
He is not Yan Xun.

348
00:18:44,550 --> 00:18:45,480
Miss Chu,

349
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:47,950
you are indeed interesting.

350
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:50,510
Unlike most people

351
00:18:50,510 --> 00:18:51,510
in this palace.

352
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:54,350
I will give you a chance.

353
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:57,030
If you don't want to marry Yan Xun,

354
00:18:57,480 --> 00:18:59,480
you can choose to stand on my side

355
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,270
and work for me.

356
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:02,820
What do you say?

357
00:19:09,030 --> 00:19:09,890
I'll marry him.

358
00:19:22,770 --> 00:19:24,030
But I have one request.

359
00:19:25,750 --> 00:19:26,950
Before I get married,

360
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,890
I want to see Li Ce one last time.

361
00:19:42,350 --> 00:19:44,070
I've told you so many times.

362
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:45,310
Don't bother me.

363
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:51,960
Fu?

364
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:54,120
You're here to see me?

365
00:19:55,070 --> 00:19:55,720
Li Ce,

366
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:58,200
you've suffered.

367
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:04,010
What are you doing here?

368
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:05,290
I don't want to see you.

369
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:06,770
You don't want to see me?

370
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:10,310
Then who was smiling so happily just now?

371
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:11,350
Who was happy?

372
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:14,790
Don't flatter yourself.

373
00:20:14,790 --> 00:20:16,070
I brought you back to Biantang

374
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:17,830
hoping you could help me.

375
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:19,240
Now look what has happened.

376
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,100
Because of you,

377
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,160
not only have I been accused

378
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,620
of colluding with Ximeng,

379
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:24,960
but I've also lost my position
as Crown Prince.

380
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,290
What are you doing here?

381
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:29,880
Get as far away from me as possible.

382
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:33,040
Don't come to bother me anymore.

383
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:43,680
Li Ce,

384
00:20:44,270 --> 00:20:46,000
I'm marrying Yan Xun tomorrow.

385
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:47,850
What did you say?

386
00:20:48,110 --> 00:20:49,640
I am going to Great Yan soon.

387
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:51,540
Is that far enough?

388
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:54,240
Qiao.

389
00:20:55,110 --> 00:20:56,070
What's going on?

390
00:20:58,830 --> 00:20:59,960
If I marry Yan Xun,

391
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:03,480
the Empress will let you leave here,

392
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,510
and you will be able to save your life.

393
00:21:05,510 --> 00:21:07,400
You may no longer be the Crown Prince,

394
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:09,160
but I didn't touch the money

395
00:21:09,790 --> 00:21:10,990
you left in that shop.

396
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:12,640
It should be enough
for the rest of your life.

397
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:14,000
Qiao, are you crazy?

398
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,030
You nearly died

399
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:16,880
escaping from Great Yan,

400
00:21:16,880 --> 00:21:18,110
and now you want to go back?

401
00:21:18,110 --> 00:21:19,830
I told you I was just using you.

402
00:21:19,830 --> 00:21:22,110
You don't need to get involved
in my affairs at all.

403
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:23,510
I left that money for you.

404
00:21:24,270 --> 00:21:25,590
Take the money and leave right away.

405
00:21:25,590 --> 00:21:26,350
Go!

406
00:21:27,270 --> 00:21:27,920
Li Ce,

407
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:30,740
I am the all-powerful,

408
00:21:31,170 --> 00:21:32,820
invincible General Chu.

409
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:34,880
Trust me.

410
00:21:35,070 --> 00:21:36,550
I will get you out of here.

411
00:22:04,030 --> 00:22:06,160
Isn't this Zhuge Yue's shadow puppet?

412
00:22:27,110 --> 00:22:27,910
Your Majesty,

413
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:30,540
we are ordered by the King of Great Yan

414
00:22:30,550 --> 00:22:32,350
to prepare your wedding makeup.

415
00:22:32,510 --> 00:22:33,920
It's not my first time.

416
00:22:38,550 --> 00:22:41,680
I am very familiar
with the wedding customs of Great Yan.

417
00:22:42,310 --> 00:22:43,720
I know what to do.

418
00:22:46,180 --> 00:22:47,570
[Boque Palace]

419
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,260
Your Highness!

420
00:23:09,160 --> 00:23:09,790
Lin Mu?

421
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:15,510
Open it!

422
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:17,580
Your Highness!

423
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:20,310
Yan Xun.

424
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:22,160
The Empress promised me

425
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:23,350
that as long as I agreed
to the marriage alliance,

426
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:24,920
my companions would be released.

427
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,650
You are going back on your word!

428
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,350
Chu,

429
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,880
this is the dowry

430
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:33,000
I requested
from the Empress for Princess Fu.

431
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:35,600
It's a long journey
from Biantang to Great Yan.

432
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:38,270
In order to prevent unexpected events,

433
00:23:38,270 --> 00:23:40,930
I have to prepare something in advance,
don't I?

434
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:43,890
Don't worry.

435
00:23:44,480 --> 00:23:45,710
Provisions in Great Yan are precious.

436
00:23:45,710 --> 00:23:46,880
We don't feed idlers.

437
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:49,650
As long as Princess Fu arrives safely
in Great Yan,

438
00:23:49,650 --> 00:23:51,510
I will release them immediately.

439
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:57,590
According to Her Majesty's decree,

440
00:23:57,590 --> 00:23:59,790
Crown Prince Li Ce has been disrespectful.

441
00:23:59,790 --> 00:24:02,030
He is stripped of his title
as Crown Prince

442
00:24:02,030 --> 00:24:03,440
and demoted to a commoner.

443
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:05,830
He is exiled to his fief in Youzhou
and confined there.

444
00:24:05,830 --> 00:24:07,510
He shall depart today.

445
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:09,750
I...

446
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:12,570
receive the decree.

447
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:21,590
Li Ce,

448
00:24:22,270 --> 00:24:23,070
trust me.

449
00:24:23,350 --> 00:24:25,410
I will definitely get you out of here.

450
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:28,410
Your Highness,

451
00:24:29,020 --> 00:24:31,400
you've been staring at this shadow puppet
all the way.

452
00:24:31,400 --> 00:24:33,240
Does it have some special meaning?

453
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:33,800
Shut up.

454
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:48,680
This shadow puppet is a secret signal
from Qiao.

455
00:24:49,350 --> 00:24:50,680
It can help us escape.

456
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:52,160
It's very important.

457
00:25:03,790 --> 00:25:05,450
Gentlemen, your tea is ready.

458
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:37,550
S-Sir.

459
00:25:37,550 --> 00:25:38,550
Your cup is full.

460
00:25:40,110 --> 00:25:40,830
Thank you.

461
00:25:40,890 --> 00:25:41,750
Enjoy your tea.

462
00:25:52,070 --> 00:25:52,930
Your Highness.

463
00:26:10,430 --> 00:26:11,500
Coming.

464
00:26:13,640 --> 00:26:14,300
Here you go.

465
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:16,400
Enjoy.

466
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:17,550
Sir.

467
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,920
It's him! It's him!

468
00:26:26,550 --> 00:26:28,650
This shadow puppet is beautifully made.

469
00:26:28,650 --> 00:26:29,510
Enjoy your tea.

470
00:26:33,310 --> 00:26:34,170
Your Highness,

471
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:35,800
it seems this shadow puppet

472
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:37,540
doesn't have any special use.

473
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:39,890
Don't worry.

474
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,720
Qiao will definitely find a way

475
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:42,510
to save us.

476
00:27:10,330 --> 00:27:11,190
Your Highness.

477
00:27:11,550 --> 00:27:12,000
Your Highness.

478
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,110
Qiao is here to save us?

479
00:27:13,110 --> 00:27:13,680
No.

480
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:16,990
This doesn't seem to be the official road.

481
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:29,270
Why did we stop?

482
00:27:30,720 --> 00:27:32,980
Don't panic. I'll go down and take a look.

483
00:27:37,750 --> 00:27:39,030
Where are they?

484
00:27:51,590 --> 00:27:52,650
Where is everyone?

485
00:27:58,480 --> 00:27:59,400
Great!

486
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,360
You're finally here!

487
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:02,480
What did I say?

488
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:05,380
I told you Qiao would definitely
come to save us.

489
00:28:05,830 --> 00:28:08,560
I'm afraid I will disappoint you,
Your Highness.

490
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:12,650
Her Majesty specifically ordered me

491
00:28:13,130 --> 00:28:15,650
to send you to hell.

492
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:17,310
No.

493
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:19,830
You have been demoted to a commoner.

494
00:28:20,030 --> 00:28:22,020
You don't deserve
to be called Your Highness anymore.

495
00:28:22,020 --> 00:28:23,200
Zhan Ziyu!

496
00:28:24,430 --> 00:28:26,170
Don't think you can do whatever you want

497
00:28:26,170 --> 00:28:27,790
just because Her Majesty
is backing you up.

498
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:29,510
The people coming to save me
will be here soon.

499
00:28:29,510 --> 00:28:31,920
I knew someone would come to save you,

500
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:34,570
so I specifically chose this road for you.

501
00:28:34,590 --> 00:28:36,110
By the time your people arrive,

502
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:38,440
they can only collect your corpse.

503
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:43,210
I am no longer the Crown Prince.

504
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,770
I will no longer pose any threat to her.

505
00:28:46,270 --> 00:28:47,130
I didn't expect

506
00:28:47,550 --> 00:28:49,270
she still wouldn't let me go.

507
00:28:49,510 --> 00:28:50,270
What a pity.

508
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:52,240
Although you are her son,

509
00:28:52,350 --> 00:28:54,510
you don't know her at all.

510
00:28:54,510 --> 00:28:55,350
You're wrong!

511
00:28:56,350 --> 00:28:57,540
I know her too well!

512
00:28:58,420 --> 00:28:59,860
I just thought that

513
00:29:01,510 --> 00:29:03,970
no matter what conflict I had
with my mother,

514
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:06,160
we were still blood,

515
00:29:07,270 --> 00:29:09,030
and things would never come to this.

516
00:29:09,030 --> 00:29:10,860
You think that to Her Majesty,

517
00:29:10,890 --> 00:29:13,170
you're only a threat to her power?

518
00:29:13,510 --> 00:29:15,030
Your very existence

519
00:29:15,030 --> 00:29:16,360
is a humiliation to her.

520
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:18,920
Only when you completely disappear

521
00:29:19,350 --> 00:29:21,000
can she truly feel at ease.

522
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:02,520
Let's see how far you can run.

523
00:30:12,110 --> 00:30:12,870
Song Cheng!

524
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:14,050
Run, Your Highness!

525
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:20,510
Run!

526
00:30:56,550 --> 00:30:57,200
Take him.

527
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,090
Minglu.

528
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:08,680
Minglu?

529
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,000
You actually...

530
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,000
Cut the crap!

531
00:31:11,780 --> 00:31:12,350
Minglu,

532
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:13,710
take them and go first.

533
00:31:13,710 --> 00:31:15,310
I still have something to do.

534
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:30,330
Assemble the troops

535
00:31:30,450 --> 00:31:31,710
and prepare to depart!

536
00:31:36,350 --> 00:31:37,880
Consort Helian is missing.

537
00:31:39,830 --> 00:31:40,590
What is it?

538
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:43,800
Your Majesty,

539
00:31:44,110 --> 00:31:45,640
Consort Helian is missing.

540
00:31:46,180 --> 00:31:46,900
Missing?

541
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:48,040
Your Majesty,

542
00:31:48,750 --> 00:31:49,750
Consort Helian

543
00:31:49,750 --> 00:31:51,440
said she was going for a walk nearby

544
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,900
and went to that hillside.

545
00:31:53,110 --> 00:31:54,550
But when the maids went to look for her,

546
00:31:54,550 --> 00:31:55,680
she was not there.

547
00:31:56,030 --> 00:31:56,680
We've already sent people

548
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:58,270
to search the entire hillside,

549
00:31:58,270 --> 00:31:59,600
but they found nothing.

550
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:00,980
Then keep looking.

551
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:03,750
Where could she possibly go alone?

552
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:04,550
Yes.

553
00:32:06,030 --> 00:32:07,200
You guys, follow me!

554
00:32:16,310 --> 00:32:17,480
Split up and search!

555
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:26,680
Go now.

556
00:32:27,030 --> 00:32:29,310
Yan Xun should only be delayed
for a short while.

557
00:32:29,310 --> 00:32:30,880
I can't go alone.

558
00:32:31,060 --> 00:32:33,790
I have to take everyone
in the prison cart with me.

559
00:32:34,030 --> 00:32:34,760
Impossible.

560
00:32:35,480 --> 00:32:36,940
I only agreed to let you go.

561
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:39,200
Those people aren't part of our deal.

562
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,030
Well now,

563
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,880
the deal has changed.

564
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:54,900
Though I'm from Great Yan,

565
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,760
I've heard that in Biantang,

566
00:32:57,160 --> 00:33:00,020
the god here governs
the love between men and women.

567
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:03,310
I pray that you bless His Majesty
so he may achieve his heart's desire

568
00:33:03,310 --> 00:33:05,840
and be happily united
with Queen Chu forever.

569
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:08,030
I am willing to spend my life
in vegetarian devotion and accumulate merit,

570
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:12,360
only in exchange for His Majesty
and his beloved being together in happiness.

571
00:33:15,750 --> 00:33:17,810
How could you believe in such a thing?

572
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:18,800
Your Majesty?

573
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:20,240
Utterly foolish.

574
00:33:21,510 --> 00:33:22,440
I am ignorant.

575
00:33:23,030 --> 00:33:26,350
I saw Your Majesty
worrying because of Queen Chu

576
00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:29,030
but didn't know how to ease your burden.

577
00:33:29,350 --> 00:33:30,880
I just heard from the mountain people
on the road

578
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:32,200
that this temple is very efficacious,

579
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:33,880
so I wanted to come up
and pay my respects.

580
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:35,480
Everyone is waiting for you.

581
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:37,110
Don't waste time.

582
00:34:14,560 --> 00:34:15,760
Run! Run!

583
00:34:15,780 --> 00:34:16,739
Hurry! Hurry!

584
00:34:17,030 --> 00:34:17,670
Let's go!

585
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:34,630
Your Majesty,

586
00:34:34,630 --> 00:34:36,590
while we were looking for Consort Helian,

587
00:34:36,590 --> 00:34:37,480
Chu Qiao escaped in the chaos.

588
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:38,630
It is my fault.

589
00:34:39,030 --> 00:34:40,830
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

590
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:05,280
Your Majesty,

591
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:06,480
it's all my fault.

592
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:08,510
If Your Majesty
hadn't been looking for me,

593
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:09,150
Her Majesty wouldn't have...

594
00:35:09,150 --> 00:35:10,750
Get in the wedding carriage.

595
00:35:11,950 --> 00:35:12,750
Your Majesty?

596
00:35:17,150 --> 00:35:19,550
I told you to get into
the wedding carriage.

597
00:35:51,670 --> 00:35:52,470
Your Majesty.

598
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:54,030
Now that Chu Qiao has run away,

599
00:35:54,030 --> 00:35:55,630
she will definitely return to Tangjing.

600
00:35:55,630 --> 00:35:57,630
Should we inform Biantang Empress?

601
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:00,400
Let's go.

602
00:36:01,610 --> 00:36:03,540
Return to the Capital of Great Yan.

603
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:14,540
Didn't we agree to meet at the residence?

604
00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:15,910
Why are you here?

605
00:36:16,150 --> 00:36:18,070
I was afraid you'd change your mind

606
00:36:18,070 --> 00:36:20,070
and go back to Great Yan with Yan Xun.

607
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:21,800
I didn't know

608
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:24,280
that Lord Zhuge could get angry too.

609
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:25,920
Couldn't you tell

610
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:27,190
I've been angry all these days?

611
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:28,450
I really couldn't.

612
00:36:29,530 --> 00:36:31,260
Whether you're angry or not,

613
00:36:31,510 --> 00:36:33,230
you always have a frozen face.

614
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,070
Chu,

615
00:36:47,910 --> 00:36:49,710
I prepared this for you.

616
00:37:04,510 --> 00:37:05,400
Do you like it?

617
00:37:19,510 --> 00:37:20,150
Chu,

618
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:23,740
let me draw your eyebrows for you.

619
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:28,710
Do you remember

620
00:37:29,510 --> 00:37:31,370
when we were in Yingge Courtyard,

621
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:33,370
I also drew your eyebrows for you?

622
00:37:37,190 --> 00:37:39,590
You promised to go back to Great Yan
with me.

623
00:37:40,670 --> 00:37:41,880
But why?

624
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:44,540
Why would you rather stay in Biantang

625
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:47,550
with that incompetent Crown Prince

626
00:37:48,550 --> 00:37:50,360
than go back with me?

627
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:55,470
Your Majesty.

628
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:57,920
Look at me.

629
00:38:02,150 --> 00:38:03,800
I am not Queen Chu.

630
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:11,610
Didn't you want to be Queen Chu?

631
00:38:12,190 --> 00:38:14,590
Haven't you always wanted to replace her?

632
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:17,000
I'm giving you the chance.

633
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:20,920
Why aren't you taking it?

634
00:38:40,590 --> 00:38:42,450
I thought you were a smart person.

635
00:38:43,190 --> 00:38:45,550
I didn't expect you to be so stupid too.

636
00:38:45,550 --> 00:38:46,360
Princess Fu!

637
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:49,670
Do you know that
holding the Empress hostage is treason?

638
00:38:50,670 --> 00:38:52,480
You, a deposed Princess,

639
00:38:52,510 --> 00:38:54,590
and me, a useless prince,

640
00:38:54,740 --> 00:38:56,570
are a match made in heaven.

641
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:57,880
You bold traitor!

642
00:38:58,170 --> 00:38:59,500
To frame me,

643
00:38:59,590 --> 00:39:01,440
you dare to hold His Majesty hostage?

